stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> queued: Agent requests payout

    queued --> policy_check: start_review
    
    policy_check --> reputation_check: pass_policy
    policy_check --> held: hold (policy violation)
    policy_check --> rejected: reject

    reputation_check --> anomaly_check: pass_reputation
    reputation_check --> held: hold (reputation risk)
    reputation_check --> rejected: reject

    anomaly_check --> approved: pass_anomaly (auto-approve)
    anomaly_check --> held: hold (anomaly detected)
    anomaly_check --> rejected: reject

    held --> pending_l1_approval: escalate_l1
    
    pending_l1_approval --> approved: approve_l1
    pending_l1_approval --> pending_l2_approval: escalate_l2
    pending_l1_approval --> rejected: reject

    pending_l2_approval --> approved: approve_l2
    pending_l2_approval --> rejected: reject

    approved --> disbursed: disburse (Razorpay)
    
    disbursed --> confirmed: confirm (webhook)
    disbursed --> failed: fail_disbursement
    
    confirmed --> archived: archive
    rejected --> archived: archive
    failed --> archived: archive
